trans-unit.source: Specifies how many times an instance of a template can be created.
trans-unit.target: Angir hvor mange ganger kan opprette en forekomst av en mal.

trans-unit.source: The TemplateInstance enumeration specifies values indicating the number of times an instance of a template can be created.
trans-unit.target: Opplistingen TemplateInstance angir verdier som angir hvor mange ganger kan opprette en forekomst av en mal.

trans-unit.source: The ttribute class uses values from the TemplateInstance enumeration.
trans-unit.target: Klassen ttribute bruker verdier fra TemplateInstance-nummerering.

trans-unit.source: In particular, the ttribute.Single and ttribute.Multiple fields specify single and multiple instances of a template, respectively.
trans-unit.target: Bestemte ttribute. Enkel og ttribute. Flere felt angi én eller flere forekomster av en mal henholdsvis.

trans-unit.source: A single instance of a template allows you to reference controls that are contained within the template.
trans-unit.target: En enkelt forekomst av en mal, kan du referere til kontroller som befinner seg i malen.

trans-unit.source: Examples of controls that use the Single value in property metadata include the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZone.ZoneTemplate%2A> property of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZone> control, the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone.ZoneTemplate%2A> property of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone> control, and the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone.ZoneTemplate%2A> property of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>.
trans-unit.target: Kontroller som bruker enkeltverdien i egenskapen metadataene eksempler på <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZone.ZoneTemplate%2A>egenskapen av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZone>kontrollen, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone.ZoneTemplate%2A>egenskapen av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone>kontrollen, og <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone.ZoneTemplate%2A>for <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone.ZoneTemplate%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone.ZoneTemplate%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZone> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZone.ZoneTemplate%2A>

trans-unit.source: A template that is instantiated multiple times.
trans-unit.target: En mal som brukes flere ganger.

trans-unit.source: A template that is instantiated only one time.
trans-unit.target: En mal som forekomstopprettet bare én gang.
